$ PowerShell: the automatic variable $args

`$args` is an → Windows/PowerShell/language/type/array that is used:
  • in → Windows/PowerShell/language/function[functions] for undeclared function → Windows/PowerShell/language/function/parameter[parameters]
  • in the `sourceArgs` property of the `psEventArgs` → Windows/PowerShell/language/object of the → Windows/PowerShell/command-inventory/noun/event/get[`get-event`] cmdLet.

{ Undeclared function parameters #ps-args-undeclared-params

 `$args` is populated in → Windows/PowerShell/language/function[functions] for *undeclared* → Windows/PowerShell/language/function/parameter[parameters].

